{"tid":2205349,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府擴大檢測　續黑箱作業　 目標100萬人　議員促招標","createTime":"2020-09-16T18:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T01:11:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"30dc9c14c8a3e83a4bd8d7deaa1cc25aa56c34c8","tid":2205349,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:17:57.000Z","msg":"政府揚言會持續擴大特定群組檢測計劃，目標檢測人數達100萬人，部份群組更會定期覆檢，惟政府至今並無交代費用細節，更無交代是否繼續「欽點」現時負責計劃的三間公司壟斷進行。有立法會議員批評政府黑箱作業，促請政府公開招標覆檢計劃及交代費用細節。<br />\n<br />\n政府上月初以疫情嚴峻、有逼切及必要性為由，以抗疫基金名義直接向華昇診斷中心、中龍檢驗認證及Prenetics三間化驗所購買特定群組檢測服務，並無交代涉及多少公帑，只披露每個檢測收費約300多元起。<br />\n<br />\n隨着疫情擴大，特定群組亦由最初的安老院舍、殘疾人士院舍及護養院、的士及小巴、食肆、街市租戶，以及物管等員工，擴展至酒店、公共交通運輸服務、長者、學校教職員，以及各政府部門的前線公務員等，政府聲稱期望檢測人數可達100萬人。以政府提供的每個檢測收費至少300元計算，三間被欽點的化驗所最少袋三億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/5A2UMSKBTFACDMERWBL2FWGBE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2F5A2UMSKBTFACDMERWBL2FWGBE4%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BrVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=07aa6fa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2F5A2UMSKBTFACDMERWBL2FWGBE4%2F&h=5f8989a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/5A2UMSKBTFACDMERWBL2FWGBE4/</a>"},{"pid":"b3b7d70fb11e2178acbe89ef14c9682ad04ac99e","tid":2205349,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1e5cc7366212ced2848aa1541e4df9b6b90998","tid":2205349,"uid":202729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:21:14.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4bced5e4a828f